== 气象历史 ==
9月22日，[[索科罗岛|索科罗岛]]东南方向出现一片强度较弱的[[热带扰动|扰动天气]]。这股扰动总体向北移动，于9月23日晚在距原位置160公里开外发展成热带低气压{{#tag:ref|根据[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]的定义，热带低气压是指[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]在每小时62公里以下的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]<ref name="glos">{{cite report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-03-25 | accessdate = 2014-06-15 | title = Glossary of NHC Terms | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601020814/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。次日，低气压继续以每小时15公里的速度北上，并增强成热带风暴{{#tag:ref|根据美国国家飓风中心的定义，热带风暴是指持续风速在每小时63至118公里之间的热带气旋<ref name="glos" />。|group="注"}}。9月24日晚，[[卫星地图|卫星图像]]显示[[大气环流|环流中心]]附近风力时速已有80公里{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，所有风速数据均为1分钟持续风速。|group="注"|name="winds"}}。热带风暴黑兹尔也在此期间达到986[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.1[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度。9月26日，有船只测得时速95公里的最强风速。风暴接下来向[[罗盘方位|东北偏东]]方向移动，于9月26日在[[马萨特兰|马萨特兰]]以南不远处[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，并在不久后转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。<ref name="Seasonal Summary">{{cite book | author = United States Weather Bureau | year = 1965 | title = Climatological Data - National Summary | pages = 72–74 | accessdate = 2015-08-11 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=izYIAAAAIAAJ&pg=PT231&dq=&hl=zh-CN | archive-date = 2019-09-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190904050642/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=izYIAAAAIAAJ&pg=PT231&dq=&hl=zh-CN | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="EPAC HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | author3 = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | date = 2014-07-07 | accessdate = 2015-08-11 | title = The Northeast and North Central Pacific hurricane database 1949–2013 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-nencpac-1949-2013-070714.txt | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141005025406/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-nencpac-1949-2013-070714.txt | archivedate = 2014-10-05 }}</ref>

== 防灾措施、影响和善后 ==
多名[[气象学|气象学家]]预计风暴会一直远离陆地，所以许多居民都对热带风暴黑兹尔缺乏准备。马萨特兰有约1万人从低洼地区撤离<ref name="San Antonio Express">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | year = 1965 | title = Storm Damage In Mexico May Exceed $10 Million | newspaper = ''San Antonio Express'' | location = San Antonio}}</ref>，该市受到严重破坏<ref name="Tucson Daily Citizen">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | year = 1965 | title = Death Count Now 6 In Mazatlan Storm | newspaper = ''Tucson Daily Citizen'' | location=Tucson}}</ref>。多条河流泛滥，约五千人无处躲避。马萨特兰全城停电，城市供水系统受损<ref name="Herald-Journal">{{cite news | title = Mexico Battered By Storm | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=XXIsAAAAIBAJ&sjid=2MsEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6186,4451457&dq=tropical+storm+hazel&hl=en | accessdate = 2015-08-11 | location = Guadalajara | newspaper = ''Herald-Journal'' | agency = Associated Press | year = 1965 | archive-date = 2016-05-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160528222308/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=XXIsAAAAIBAJ&sjid=2MsEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6186,4451457&dq=tropical+storm+hazel&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。至少有五十艘船因风暴受损或沉没。估计整场风暴造成的损失至少有一千万美元（1965年美元），黑兹尔因此成为1965年太平洋飓风季中破坏最严重的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]<ref name="Seasonal Summary" /><ref name="San Antonio Express" />。马萨特兰有三人丧生，其中有两名渔夫在风暴期间遇难，还有一个男孩因输电线缆斷裂导致触电身亡，[[纳亚里特州|纳亚里特州]]也有三人触电而死。受通讯中断的影响，六名正在马萨特兰度假的游客音讯全无，<ref name="Tucson Daily Citizen" />外界只能通过船只同该市取得联系<ref name="The Spokesmen-Review">{{cite news | title = Storm-Hit, Mexicans Get Aid, Coastal | agency = Associated Press | location = Guadalajara | year = 1965 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=wDpWAAAAIBAJ&sjid=TekDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5873,4323705&dq=tropical+storm+hazel&hl=en | accessdate = 2015-08-11 | newspaper = ''The Spokesmen-Review'' | archive-date = 2016-05-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160527051556/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=wDpWAAAAIBAJ&sjid=TekDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5873,4323705&dq=tropical+storm+hazel&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此外，多个以木材、锡皮和硬纸板搭建的窝棚被1.8米高的泥水冲走或淹没，风暴产生的洪水还冲毁了该州各地的许多桥梁和道路<ref name="Tucson Daily Citizen" /><ref name="Sarasota Herald-Tribune">{{cite news | title = Pacific Storm Batters Mexican Coastal Area | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1774&dat=19650928&id=A7kqAAAAIBAJ&sjid=uGUEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6525,5425595&hl=zh-CN | accessdate = 2015-08-11 | location = Guadalajara | newspaper = ''Sarasota Herald-Tribune'' | agency = Associated Press | year = 1965 | archive-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210120131030/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1774&dat=19650928&id=A7kqAAAAIBAJ&sjid=uGUEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6525%2C5425595&hl=zh-CN | dead-url = no }}</ref>。马萨特兰的捕虾船队是该市的经济基础，因此气旋对该州沿海经济造成重大影响。[[锡那罗亚州|锡那罗亚州]]南部有220平方公里的棉花、玉米和高粱绝收<ref name="Tucson Daily Citizen" />。报道还表明当地损失了大量牲畜<ref name="San Antonio Express" />。

风暴过后，有约1000人前往学校寻求庇护，巴伦和韦拉莫乡村地区的居民只能在树上或屋顶躲避<ref name="San Antonio Express" />。军队和[[救灾机构|救灾机构]]匆忙赶赴多个沿海城市提供援助<ref name="Herald-Journal" />。由于风暴造成了严重影响，其名称“黑兹尔”（{{lang|en|Hazel}}）因此除名，今后永远都不会再在东太平洋风暴命名时采用。用于取代的新名称是“希瑟”（{{lang|en|Heather}}），于[[1969年太平洋飓风季|1969年]]启用<ref name="AOML FAQ">{{cite web | author = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | year = 2009 | title = Subject: B3) What names have been retired in the Atlantic and East Pacific basin? | accessdate = 2015-08-11 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/B3.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150701194456/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/B3.html | archivedate = 2015-07-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

